I've been playing mostly alts that are non pet classes, so I can't speak to the pet buff issue.  But I think there'd be a huge problem if sprint didn't drain power.  If sprint didn't drain from some kind of pool (power, endurance, whatever), then there would be no encounter in the game you couldn't get away from.
<br />

<br />
If you talk to many of the NPCs in the game, they each have a little bit of the puzzle of the story of the new Norrath.  They explain very well, in bits and pieces, why most combat arts are arcane in nature.  So they actually have some backstory for it too.<br />_________________<br />EQ1:  Mujahid Mukhtaar - Arch Lich, Solusek Ro (Retired)
